<author>Thangngur</author>
<title>Lei Ah Cham Leng Hen</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zankhanglai a belampu,
 Bethlehem phulah giekhaw kha;
 Van lam thilgin a hun thawn,
 Ngai dingin a tho ui;
 Kipahna huih a nung hieuhieu.
 Angel aw a git laiin;
 Mitin dinga pahchak tak Lal,
 Krista pienna thu gen in;
 &quot;Lei ah cham leng hen&quot; tin.

[V2]
 2. Van lal cha va en tiem u,
 Bethlehem bawng In sung achun;
 A chunnu liengthei Mari'n,
 Gankuong sungah a siel;
 Chung si-al a hung vak singseng.
 Gankuong zalkhun zawn chungah;
 Suohlam michingten a hun zui,
 A go bawmteu hun chawiin;
 Lal chibai a pieu ie.

[V3]
 3. Ziehi ahi van thug gen,
 Namtin chitinte tatna di'n;
 A khut leh keng a kilh in,
 A nak ah sun unau;
 Hinna damtui in luong intin,
 Aw Kalvari tang chung ah;
 Chun khawvel ah luong zak intin,
 Thiemgau thu genlawk bangin;
 Namtin sukdamna di'n.</lyrics>
</song>